<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/p5.js/1.0.0/p5.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://unpkg.com/ml5@latest/dist/ml5.min.js"></script>
<script>
function dispmsg()
{
alert("scanning")
}</script>
<body style="background-color:black">
<h1 style="color:white">Image Classification</h1>
<h2 style="color:white">With MobileNet and ml5.js</h2>
<input type="button" value="Click Me to Scan" onClick="dispmsg()">
<br><br>
<div style="color:white"id="result">Scanning</div>
<br>
<img height="50%" width="50%" id="image" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," width="100%">

<script>
// Initialize Image Classifier with MobileNet.
const classifier =  ml5.imageClassifier('MobileNet');
classifier.classify(document.getElementById("image"), gotResult);

// Function to run when results arrive
function gotResult(error, results) {
  const element = document.getElementById("result");
  if (error) {
    element.innerHTML = error;
  } else {
    let num = results[0].confidence * 100;
    element.innerHTML = results[0].label + "<br>Confidence: " + num.toFixed(2) + "%";
  }
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
